            yield return lineBreak();
            yield return lineBreak();
            yield return text(@"And yet, set upon by the emotional heft of this abomination, I felt at once reinvigorated. For while love in its most passionate form was known to revive the soul, it is hate which raises the blood to the cheeks and sets the mind to precise action. I spoke a curse so vile I felt the lilacs wilt at the base of the wretched monument and spate upon the ground thrice.");
